{"title":"海南短歌","authors":["芦获"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南短歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榆林港边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条公路如弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直达榆林港边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山海绵延不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山响涛音交缠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对海一时无语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大洋气象万千；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个小小泡沫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准敌人污染。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三亚港远眺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在三亚港边："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天涯”在面前，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮涌新沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波浪拍天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年的苏东坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立马临海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手题“南荒”，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北望中原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在三亚港边："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天涯”非从前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舰艇翩翩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处一片歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日蛮烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日花园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：宋苏东坡曾在三亚港边，题下“天涯”及“南荒一柱”六字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌五指山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙境还是人间？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层楼碧树青山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我欲增添一笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深浅浓淡都难；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣看巨灵一掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指插入云间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957.2．于海南"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}